Modbus Translation Example (C):

```c
// modbus_bridge.c
void translate_to_modbus(uint32_t st_output, uint16_t modbus_register) {
    // Scale from 0-2^32 to 0-65535
    uint16_t scaled = (st_output >> 16) & 0xFFFF;
    
    // Write to Modbus holding register (via UART/RS-485)
    modbus_write_holding_register(modbus_register, scaled);
    
    // Set watchdog timestamp
    last_transmission = get_timestamp();
}
